  "keyFeatures": [
    "Dependency-free NPM package for client-side use",
    "PPP-adjusted pricing calculation using World Bank data",
    "Flexible smoothing parameter (0-1) to normalize discounts",
    "Three rounding strategies: none, currency, and marketing-friendly pretty",
    "Support for both 2-letter and 3-letter ISO country codes",
    "Direct access to raw Price Level Ratio factors",
    "TypeScript type definitions included"
